remove

void remove()
Remove the SbbEntity (Spec. 5.5.4) It detaches the SBB entity from all Activity Contexts. It invokes the appropriate life cycle methods (see Section 6.3) of an SBB object that caches the SBB entity's state. It removes the SBB entity from the ChildRelation object that the SBB entity belongs to. It removes the persistent representation of the SBB entity.
